<div class = "progress">
AGE:<strong><% (age = (( Time.now - @profile.dob.to_time ) / 1.years).to_i) %><%= age %></strong>
<br />


<% if @profile.cache_current_weight.to_i == 0 then %>
  <br />Please enter your initial body measurements: <%= link_to 'Body Image', new_measurement_path %>.  Thank you.<br />
  
  
<% else %>



<% if @profile.cache_current_weight_goal.to_i == 0 %>
<br />  Please go to body measurements, and put your goals and make sure 'Is goal' is checked: <%= link_to 'Body Image', new_measurement_path %> :.  Thank you.<br />

<% else %>

Weight: <strong><%= @profile.cache_current_weight %></strong> 
Goal Weight: <strong><%= @profile.cache_current_weight_goal %></strong><br /> Goal accomplishment: <strong><%  to_goal =  (@profile.cache_current_weight_goal.to_f / @profile.cache_current_weight) *100 %><%= to_goal.to_i %>%</strong><br />
